    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 58-61.</p><p>Killing Strikes</p><p>Starting at 23rd level, your hunting skills and your magic have made you deadlier than any other at dispatching your foes. Your critical range is increased by 1. When you hit critically, you deal Lethal damage instead of your normal damage type. In addition, when you hit a creature with an attack and that creature has 50 or fewer hit points remaining, you can choose to reduce it to 0 hit points.</p></div>",
